(365, 24, 48, 'One of my strong beliefs is that data is a great driver of growth &amp; change.\r\n\r\nWe can deliver high added clients value &amp; better customer experience by crafting our strategies on data centric approaches &amp; innovative technologies.\r\n\r\nThis conviction is born from more than 25 years of experience running core areas of banking consulting, financial &amp; banking areas at international level.\r\n\r\nMy diverse career led me to become Chief Data Officer at BNP Paribas International Retail Banking (IRB).\r\n\r\nWith our great teams based in Paris &amp; trough EMEA, US &amp; African regions, we are driving data transformation programs, implementing new process, integrating new teams, deploying operational efficiencies models, building big &amp; data centric architecture and new way of working together.\r\n\r\nAs being the champion of data transformation, I’m keenly engaged with my teams to build data driven organization and data driven business models that contribute to position BNP Paribas IRB as an international reference for innovative services &amp; products for our clients.\r\n\r\nAs a Change Management leader, I’m convinced that transversal collaboration and a high level of commitment are key enablers of success &amp; performances of our company.\r\n\r\nSpecialities:\r\n\r\n• Business Transformation Leadership, Change Management agent\r\n\r\n• International Management\r\n\r\n• Operating models\r\n\r\n• New technologies. Artificial Intelligence.\r\n\r\n• Data strategy, data architecture, data analytics, data science, data operations\r\n\r\n• Data mining, segmentation, statistics, predictive data models\r\n\r\n• Big data\r\n\r\n• IT architecture.\r\n\r\n• Lean and Six-Sigma Practitioner\r\n\r\n• Compliance, regulation\r\n\r\n• Retail Banking, Asset Management, Corporate and Investment\r\n\r\n• New ways of working', '2018-10-23 17:51:12'),
