uccess. Creating a [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/">9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"Editorial Team";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17619:"<p>Do you want the best real estate plugins for your WordPress website? Real estate websites are a fantastic business generator as they support tools and features to make property deals online.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share 9 of the best WordPress real estate plugins you can use to make your website a success.</p>\n<h3>Creating a Real Estate Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most flexible and popular website builder on the market. Many of <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/" title="46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively">the world&#8217;s top brands are using WordPress</a> for their websites.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 kinds of WordPress websites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. For more details, see our side-by-side comparison on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/" title="WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>For a real estate website, you should use self-hosted WordPress.org. It&#8217;s highly flexible and offers amazing features to develop powerful websites.</p>\n<p>Before starting, you&#8217;ll need to buy a domain name and a web hosting account to install WordPress properly.</p>\n<p>Bluehost is our recommended web hosting solution. It&#8217;s one of the most popular hosting companies and is officially recommended by WordPress&#8217; core.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering IsItWP readers a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg" alt="create a blog on bluehost" width="775" height="483" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-218254" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></p>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="btn ltgreen light">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>After purchasing web hosting, you can follow our step-by-step guide on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/" title="How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)">how to create a WordPress website</a>.</p>\n<p>Having said that, let&#8217;s take a look at the best WordPress real estate plugins.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-pro/" target="_blank" title="Real Estate Pro" rel="nofollow">1. Real Estate Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/real-estate-pro/" target="_blank" title="Real Estate Pro" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro.jpg" alt="Real Estate Pro" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223541" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/realestatepro-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Real Estate Pro is a premium WordPress real estate and property listing plugin. It enables your users to add their listings, claim listings, sell properties, manage client reviews, and more. Your website&#8217;s visitors can bid for the properties, leave a note for the listing owner, contact property owners, and <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/tips-get-email-subscribers/" title="23 Effective Tips to Get More Email Subscribers Today">subscribe to your lists</a> to get regular updates.</p>\n<p>The plugin&#8217;s translation-ready and fully supports <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpml/" target="_blank" title="WPML" rel="nofollow">WPML</a>. It also supports third-party services like Stripe, PayPal, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mailchimp/" target="_blank" title="MailChimp" rel="nofollow">MailChimp</a>, etc. </p>\n<p>Real Estate Pro is integrated with <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/visual-composer-website-builder/" target="_blank" title="Visual Composer" rel="nofollow">Visual Composer</a> to quickly set up your property website and <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/" title="30 Ways to Make Money Online Blogging (On the Side) in 2018">start making money online</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/estatik/" target="_blank" title="Estatik" rel="nofollow">2. Estatik</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/estatik/" target="_blank" title="Estatik" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik.jpg" alt="Estatik" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223540" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/estatik-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Estatik is a free WordPress real estate plugin that can be used to add property listings on your website. You can use this plugin to create and manage fully functional real estate solutions with ease.</p>\n<p>It offers language support, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/google-maps-builder/" title="Google Maps Builder Review: Easily Embed Interactive Maps">Google Maps</a> integration, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/" title="12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)">social media</a> icons, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/" title="7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)">an image gallery</a>, real estate widget, and more. It comes with unlimited options for your property listings so you can customize and sell the properties online.</p>\n<p>Estatik has advanced filters in the search for dates, famous properties, pricing, and location. It&#8217;s a fully customizable plugin and works great with all the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/" title="The Best and Most Popular WordPress Themes of 2018 (UPDATED)">top WordPress themes</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-listings/" target="_blank" title="IMPress Listings" rel="nofollow">3. IMPress Listings</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-listings/" target="_blank" title="IMPress Listings" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings.jpg" alt="IMPress listings" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223542" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/impresslistings-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>IMPress Listings is a popular WordPress plugin for real estate websites. It offers a complete solution for beginners to advanced users to launch an online real estate business.</p>\n<p>It allows your users to add their listings with images and videos of the properties. The visual impact increases traffic on your real estate website and helps with <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-seo-tools-to-grow-your-site-traffic/" title="9 Best SEO Tools to Grow Your Website Traffic, FAST!">improving SEO</a>. You can easily customize the property listings and design beautiful listing pages with complete details, Google maps, and contact information of the listing&#8217;s owner.</p>\n<p>It fully supports IDX listing and you can also import listings from other sources. It recommends a few companion plugins to include additional features to make a truly powerful real estate website.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-amortization-calculator/" target="_blank" title="WP Amortization Calculator" rel="nofollow">4. WP Amortization Calculator</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-amortization-calculator/" target="_blank" title="WP Amortization Calculator" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc.jpg" alt="WP Amortization Calculator" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223544" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpamortizationcalc-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Amortization Calculator is a premium WordPress plugin used to calculate mortgages, loans, and property financing online. It has features go above and beyond a simple mortgage calculator. It supports a lead capture tool, real estate listings, agents portal, custom property pages, email notifications, and more.</p>\n<p>It also enables you to use currency symbols and different money format choices. The <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/" title="7 Best Drag and Drop WordPress Page Builders Compared (2018)">drag and drop builder</a> support allows you to add a sophisticated amortization calculator anywhere on your real estate website.</p>\n<p>It has a custom widget that can be added in your widget areas. It&#8217;s translation-ready and includes flexible options to automatically calculate amortized loans.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-property/" target="_blank" title="WP-Property" rel="nofollow">5. WP-Property</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-property/" target="_blank" title="WP-Property" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty.jpg" alt="WP Property" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223545" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpproperty-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WP-Property is a free real estate WordPress plugin. It has the options to add property listings, manage listings, and more. It includes powerful custom options to add complete details for each property listing, like yhe number of rooms, bathrooms, capacity, parking, and other features of the property.</p>\n<p>You can create stylish property listing pages with Google Maps, real estate search, featured listings, search filters, and <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-tutorials/how-to-create-an-idx-real-estate-website-using-wordpress/" target="_blank" title="IDX listing support">IDX listing support</a>. It suggests free WordPress real estate themes and also works great with all other themes.</p>\n<p>It has widgets, shortcodes, and other methods to show real estate listings anywhere on your WordPress website. WP-Property is a flexible plugin with translation support and it&#8217;s optimized for SEO.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/essential-real-estate/" target="_blank" title="Essential Real Estate" rel="nofollow">6. Essential Real Estate</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/essential-real-estate/" target="_blank" title="Essential Real Estate" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate.jpg" alt="Essential real estate" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223547" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/essentialrealestate-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a real estate plugin that allows frontend property listing submissions, then Essential Real Estate plugin is perfect. It has both backend and frontend support for listing submissions with a powerful dashboard for agents to manage their listings.</p>\n<p>It enables you to easily customize and set up a real estate website with all the features you need. Essential Real Estate plugin supports all global <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-stripe-payment-plugins-for-wordpress/" title="6 Best Stripe Payment Plugins for WordPress (2018)">payment methods</a> so you can build a real estate market online.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/" target="_blank" title="BirchPress" rel="nofollow">7. BirchPress</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/birchpress/" target="_blank" title="BirchPress" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress.jpg" alt="BirchPress" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223548" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/birchpress-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>BirchPress is a WordPress <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/make-appointment-booking-system-wordpress/" title="How to Make an Appointment Booking System with WordPress">appointment booking and scheduling</a> plugin. It can be used as an addon on your real estate website to manage appointments between clients and agents.</p>\n<p>It allows you to easily <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-booking-plugins-compared/" title="7 Best WordPress Booking Plugins Compared (2018)">add a booking form</a> on your WordPress website and also integrates online payments through PayPal. It fully supports <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/" target="_blank" title="WooCommerce" rel="nofollow">WooCommerce</a> and all its features, so you can easily sell properties online.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpcasa/" target="_blank" title="WPCasa" rel="nofollow">8. WPCasa</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpcasa/" target="_blank" title="WPCasa" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa.jpg" alt="WPCasa" width="775" height="300" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223549" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpcasa-768x297.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WPCasa is a real estate plugin for WordPress websites. It features multiple themes that can be used to create a fully flexible and powerful real estate platform for users. WPCasa has an easy-to-use interface and all the settings are simple to manage in WordPress.</p>\n<p>It supports an advanced search engine with multiple filters to quickly find property listings on your real estate website. You can use the WPCasa editor to add property information, location maps, image galleries, and more details about your listings easily.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/real-estate-listing-realtyna-wpl/" target="_blank" title="WPL Real Estate" rel="nofollow">9. WPL Real Estate</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/real-estate-listing-realtyna-wpl/" target="_blank" title="WPL Real Estate" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate.jpg" alt="WPL real estate" width="775" height="299" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223550" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate-300x116.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wplrealestate-768x296.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WPL Real Estate is another free real estate solution for WordPress websites. It features a filterable search for users to find property listings. It offers a flexible frontend dashboard for users and agents to add their listing quickly. WPL Real Estate has the options for users to add their personal profile, property locations with Google maps, create stylish listings, custom fields, and more.</p>\n<p>It works great with all the most <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/" title="25 Must Have WordPress Plugins for Business Websites (Expert Pick)">popular WordPress plugins</a> and supports IDX listings in the premium version. You can reach out to the plugin&#8217;s developer to get custom features on request.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress real estate plugins. You should also check out our hand-picked list of the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-event-plugins/" title="9 Best WordPress Events Plugins Compared (2018)">best WordPress event plugins</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/">9 Best WordPress Real Estate Plugins COMPARED (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-real-estate-plugins/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"9 Best WordPress Job Board Plugins and Themes (Compared)";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:63:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:71:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 31 Oct 2018 08:36:27 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Resources";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"best wordpress job board themes";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"job board plugins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:28:"job board plugins and themes";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16:"job board themes";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:27:"wordpress job board plugins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222561";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:589:"<p>Do you want the best WordPress job board plugins and themes? Job board WordPress plugins and themes can be used to build a job portal or search engine for job listings easily. It helps you post new job openings and you can also allow other employers to add jobs on your blog. In this article, [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/">9 Best WordPress Job Board Plugins and Themes (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"Editorial Team";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:16304:"<p>Do you want the best WordPress job board plugins and themes? Job board WordPress plugins and themes can be used to build a job portal or search engine for job listings easily. It helps you post new job openings and you can also allow other employers to add jobs on your blog.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best WordPress job board plugins and themes so you can spend less time searching for the right tools and more time putting them into action.</p>\n<h3>Creating a Job Board Using WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the best website builder in the world. Many of the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/" title="46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively">biggest brands use WordPress</a> for their websites. It&#8217;s super flexible and offers all of the amazing features you&#8217;ll need to build your own job board.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find 2 kinds of WordPress websites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. You can view our side-by-side comparison on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/" title="WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?">WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org</a> for more details.</p>\n<p>We recommend you use WordPress.org. It&#8217;s a complete solution with access to all the most incredible features you need to succeed.</p>\n<p>But, first, you&#8217;ll need a <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/" title="What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)">domain name and web hosting</a>.</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/" target="_blank" title="Bluehost" rel="nofollow">Bluehost</a> is our recommended hosting solution. It&#8217;s one of the top web hosting companies, and also WordPress core&#8217;s official hosting partner.</p>\n<p>For our users, they&#8217;re offering a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg" alt="create a blog on bluehost" width="775" height="483" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-218254" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></p>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="btn ltgreen light">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Upon purchasing web hosting, you should follow our guide on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/" title="How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)">how to make a website</a> with WordPress.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s take a look at some of the best WordPress job board plugins and themes that you can install on your site.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-job-hunter/" target="_blank" title="Job Hunter" rel="nofollow">1. WP Job Hunter</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-job-hunter/" target="_blank" title="Job Hunter" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter.jpg" alt="WP Job Hunter" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222574" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobhunter-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Job Hunter is a WordPress job board plugin suitable to display jobs on your website or blog. You can also <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/" title="30 Ways to Make Money Online Blogging (On the Side) in 2018">make money online</a> by allowing paid job listings. It comes with a job portal widget that you can drag and drop in any of the widget-ready areas of your site to easily display jobs wherever you desire.</p>\n<p>It includes many custom and automated integrations that&#8217;ll make the setup process easy for you. It supports the most popular social media platforms, including Facebook, to add like and share features. WP Job Hunter also integrates with Google Maps to display the locations of the jobs to your users.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/jobsearch/" target="_blank" title="JobSearch" rel="nofollow">2. JobSearch</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/jobsearch/" target="_blank" title="JobSearch" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch.jpg" alt="JobSearch" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222575" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobsearch-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>JobSearch is a premium WordPress job board plugin. It features job alerts, application tracking, a resume builder, social app logins, and more. It comes with an effective search tool that makes the job searching effortless for your users.</p>\n<p>It offers employers the ability to post complete details for each job, and candidates can shortlist the jobs of their choice. Your users can apply for jobs using social media platforms like Facebook and LinkedIn. It&#8217;s a translation-ready plugin and fully supports <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/" target="_blank" title="WooCommerce" rel="nofollow">WooCommerce</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-jobengine/" target="_blank" title="JobEngine" rel="nofollow">3. JobEngine</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-jobengine/" target="_blank" title="JobEngine" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine.jpg" alt="JobEngine" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222576" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobengine-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>JobEngine is a simple WordPress job board theme. It has all the features that you need to create a job portal. It&#8217;s highly customizable and flexible, allowing you to add new job listings easily. You can also allow employers to add their jobs on your website. For this, you can create multiple packages and charge them for each listing.</p>\n<p>It supports featured listing templates, payment gateways, multiple color schemes, custom theme options, sidebars, built-in landing pages, and more. It allows you to easily <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/" title="How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)">create a multilingual website</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/appthemes-jobroller/" target="_blank" title="JobRoller" rel="nofollow">4. JobRoller</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/appthemes-jobroller/" target="_blank" title="JobRoller" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller.jpg" alt="JobRoller" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222577" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobroller-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>JobRoller is an excellent job board theme for WordPress websites. It ships with multiple sections for featured job listings, monetization options, landing pages, and an Ajax-based search filter.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, it&#8217;s easy to set up and includes custom theme options. JobRoller allows you and your users to create an account, upload job listings, manage a CV bank, and more. It&#8217;s a powerful WordPress theme for the job portals with simple, tidy layout.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-job-manager/" target="_blank" title="WP Job Manager" rel="nofollow">5. WP Job Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-job-manager/" target="_blank" title="WP Job Manager" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager.jpg" alt="WP Job Manager" width="775" height="360" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222578" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager-300x139.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobmanager-768x357.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Job Manager is a flexible WordPress job board plugin with amazing features. It allows you to easily create a job board with needed pages, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/custom-user-registration-form-wordpress/" title="How to Create a Custom User Registration Form in WordPress">user registration</a> form, and job listings. It offers a custom dashboard for your users to upload new jobs, manage listings, and more.</p>\n<p>It comes with multiple addons. It integrates your job board with Facebook, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/" target="_blank" title="WooCommerce" rel="nofollow">WooCommerce</a>, Indeed, and other useful apps.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/job-board-manager/" target="_blank" title="Job Board Manager" rel="nofollow">6. Job Board Manager</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/job-board-manager/" target="_blank" title="Job Board Manager" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager.jpg" alt="Job Board Manager" width="775" height="380" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222579" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager-300x147.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/jobboardmanager-768x377.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Job Board Manager is a free WordPress job board plugin that can be used to launch your job portal quickly. It features company profiles, Geo locations, custom widgets, and premium addons. It allows you to add the job listings on multiple pages and posts using shortcodes.</p>\n<p>Moreover, you can add new job listings, create paid listing sections, manage job alerts, and more. It supports Schema.org rich snippets, a job application dashboard, WooCommerce stores, and breadcrumbs.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/apply-online/" target="_blank" title="Apply Online" rel="nofollow">7. Apply Online</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/apply-online/" target="_blank" title="Apply Online" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline.jpg" alt="Apply Online" width="775" height="385" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222580" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/applyonline-768x382.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Apply Online is a WordPress job board plugin that lets users apply for jobs online. It&#8217;s suitable for classified ads management, accepts job applications, allows users to apply for jobs online, and sends email alerts.</p>\n<p>It comes with search filters, job listing categories, online <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-job-application-form-wordpress/" title="How to Create a Job Application Form in WordPress (Step by Step)">job application forms</a>, and custom job ads. There&#8217;s no facility to add paid listings, so you&#8217;ll need to use a companion plugin that offers paid subscriptions. You can also <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/add-contact-form-wordpress-website/" title="How to Add a Contact Form to Your WordPress Website">create a contact form</a> to receive applications from employers for custom listings.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board/" target="_blank" title="Simple Job Board" rel="nofollow">8. Simple Job Board</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/simple-job-board/" target="_blank" title="Simple Job Board" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard.jpg" alt="Simple Job Board" width="775" height="385" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222581" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard-300x149.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplejobboard-768x382.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for a simple, easy solution to add a job portal onto your WordPress site, then try Simple Job Board plugin. It gives you a full control of your job listings. The plugin&#8217;s not bloated with features. You&#8217;ll need to manually create job listings, add categories, and more. It doesn&#8217;t allow your users to create an account or add paid listings, so you&#8217;ll need to create a form on your website to accept offers from employers.</p>\n<p>With all the limitations comes flexibility as it gives you access to add complete details for job listings, show custom application forms to candidates, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wpjobboard.net/" target="_blank" title="WPJobBoard" rel="nofollow">9. WPJobBoard</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wpjobboard.net/" target="_blank" title="WPJobBoard" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard.jpg" alt="WP Job Board" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222582" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpjobboard-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WPJobBoard is a powerful WordPress plugin to create a job board on your blog. It comes with a custom portal for employers to look at the new applications and select the best candidates. It has a front-end panel that allows users to <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-file-upload-form-wordpress-step-step/" title="How to Create a File Upload Form in WordPress – (Step by Step)">upload files</a> like CVs, add new job listings, and more.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s bundled with a free job board theme that can be used to easily create a job portal website. It&#8217;s also fully flexible with the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/" title="50+ Best Responsive WordPress Themes">best WordPress themes</a>. It supports payment gateways, memberships, discounts, coupons, and <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/coupons/" title="Top Coupons &#038; Deals From Our Favorite Stores">deals</a>.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best WordPress job board plugins and themes. You may also want to see our expert pick of the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-vpn-services-wordpress-users-compared/" title="7 Best VPN Services for WordPress Users COMPARED (2018)">best VPN services for WordPress users</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/">9 Best WordPress Job Board Plugins and Themes (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:68:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-job-board-plugins-themes/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"19 Best WordPress Plugins for Non-profits &amp; Charities";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 30 Oct 2018 06:52:01 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"WordPress Plugins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:37:"best wordpress plugins for nonprofits";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:22:"plugins for nonprofits";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:44:"plugins for nonprofits to support your cause";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"wordpress plugins";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"wordpress plugins for nonprofits";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222689";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:618:"<p>Do you want the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to add features on your site? Nonprofits need WordPress plugins that can support their cause and help them build a website on a tight budget. The perfect plugins allow nonprofits to launch their website without hiring any developer, so they can save money for what really [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/">19 Best WordPress Plugins for Non-profits &#038; Charities</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"Editorial Team";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:27769:"<p>Do you want the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to add features on your site? Nonprofits need WordPress plugins that can support their cause and help them build a website on a tight budget. The perfect plugins allow nonprofits to launch their website without hiring any developer, so they can save money for what really matters: their cause.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits to support your cause.</p>\n<h3>Making a Nonprofits Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the most popular website builder in the world. You&#8217;ve likely noticed many of the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/" title="46 Biggest Brands in the World Using WordPress Actively">biggest brands in the world using WordPress actively</a> on their sites.</p>\n<p>When starting, you&#8217;ll encounter 2 types of WordPress sites: WordPress.com, which is a hosted platform; and WordPress.org, which is a self-hosted solution. See our detailed comparison between <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/" title="WordPress.com vs. WordPress.org – Is One Really Better Than the Other?">WordPress.com vs WordPress.org</a> for more information.</p>\n<p>For your site, we recommend using self-hosted WordPress.org as it has all the features and options you&#8217;ll need. If you&#8217;re already using WordPress.com, then you can <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-move-your-site-from-wordpress-com-to-wordpress-org/" title="How to Move Your Site From WordPress.com to WordPress.org">move your site from WordPress.com to WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>But, first, you&#8217;ll need a <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/" title="What’s the Difference Between Domain Name and Web Hosting? (REVEALED)">domain name and web hosting</a>.</p>\n<p>We recommend <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/" target="_blank" title="Bluehost" rel="nofollow">Bluehost</a>. It&#8217;s officially recommended by WordPress core, and 1 of the popular web hosting companies in the world.</p>\n<p>Luckily, they&#8217;re offering our users a free domain name, free SSL certificate, and a massive discount on web hosting.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg" alt="create a blog on bluehost" width="775" height="483" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-218254" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></p>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="btn ltgreen light">Click Here to Claim This Exclusive Bluehost Offer &raquo;</a></p>\n<p>Once purchased, you can follow our step-by-step guide on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/" title="How to Make a Website in 2018- Step by Step (with Pictures)">how to make a website</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, let&#8217;s take a look at the best WordPress plugins for nonprofits you can use on your WordPress site.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wpforms.com/" target="_blank" title="WPForms">1. WPForms</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wpforms.com/" target="_blank" title="WPForms"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg" alt="WPForms" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222076" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WPForms is the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/" title="7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)">best WordPress contact form plugin</a>. It&#8217;s super flexible and comes with great features to add a contact form, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-donation-form/" title="How to Create a WordPress Donation Form (Step by Step)">donation form</a>, and other useful forms on your WordPress site.</p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpforms-lite/" target="_blank" title="WPForms Lite" rel="nofollow">WPForms Lite</a> is the free version of the plugin. It can be used by <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-small-business-website-simple-steps/" title="How to Create a Small Business Website in 5 Simple Steps (2018)">small business websites</a>, nonprofits, and blogs to add a simple contact form easily. Their paid version comes with more features and options like payment addons. </p>\n<p>WPForms integrates with all the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-email-marketing-services-compared/" title="9 Best Email Marketing Services Compared (2018)">best email marketing services</a> like <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/aweber/" target="_blank" title="AWeber" rel="nofollow">AWeber</a>, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mailchimp/" target="_blank" title="MailChimp" rel="nofollow">MailChimp</a>, <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/constant-contact/" target="_blank" title="Constant Contact" rel="nofollow">Constant Contact</a>, and more.</p>\n<p>It also works great with payment services like PayPal and Stripe to collect online donations.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.monsterinsights.com/" target="_blank" title="MonsterInsights">2. MonsterInsights</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.monsterinsights.com/" target="_blank" title="MonsterInsights"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights.jpg" alt="MonsterInsights" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222077" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/monsterinsights-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>MonsterInsights is the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-analytics-solutions-compared/" title="7 Best WordPress Analytics Solutions Compared (2018)">best WordPress analytics solution</a> on the market. It shows your website traffic stats in your WordPress dashboard. MonsterInsights has many powerful addons to customize the Google Analytics reports for your site.</p>\n<p>They offer multiple pricing plans for small-to-big websites which means you can easily use MonsterInsights on your nonprofit website to add Google Analytics in WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/givewp/" target="_blank" title="GiveWP" rel="nofollow">3. GiveWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/givewp/" target="_blank" title="GiveWP" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp.jpg" alt="GiveWP" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222707" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/givewp-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>GiveWP is an excellent WordPress nonprofits plugin. It comes with all the features you&#8217;ll need to accept online donations, manage the money given, and more within your WordPress dashboard. You can easily create a donation form and integrate a payment gateway to collect donations from users.</p>\n<p>Speaking of payment gateways, GiveWP can be easily connected with the most popular payment services, like PayPal. On top of that, you can also connect your donation form with the popular email services, including AWeber and MailChimp.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://optinmonster.com/" target="_blank" title="OptinMonster">4. OptinMonster</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://optinmonster.com/" target="_blank" title="OptinMonster"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster.jpg" alt="OptinMonster" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222709" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/optinmonster-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>OptinMonster is the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-lead-generation-plugins-compared/" title="7 Best WordPress Lead Generation Plugins Compared (2018)">best WordPress lead generation plugin</a> in the world. You can use this plugin on your nonprofit site to make sure visitors donate to your cause before leaving your site.</p>\n<p>It offers multiple optin popup styles including slide in, sidebar, lightbox, and more. OptinMonster has helped many businesses and nonprofits to grow their subscribers exponentially.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/" target="_blank" title="Easy Digital Downloads" rel="nofollow">5. Easy Digital Downloads</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/easy-digital-downloads/" target="_blank" title="Easy Digital Downloads" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads.jpg" alt="Easy Digital Downloads" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222708" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/easydigitaldownloads-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Easy Digital Downloads is one of the most popular <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/" title="7 Best WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared (2018)">WordPress eCommerce plugins</a>. It allows you to sell digital downloads, like eBooks, to collect money for your nonprofit cause. </p>\n<p>Easy Digital Downloads has powerful addons to integrate payment gateways, services, and more.</p>\n<p>It works great on all the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/" title="The Best and Most Popular WordPress Themes of 2018 (UPDATED)">best WordPress themes</a>. It&#8217;s flexible and easy to set up on your site.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/" target="_blank" title="WP Super Cache" rel="nofollow">6. WP Super Cache</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/" target="_blank" title="WP Super Cache" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache.jpg" alt="WP Super Cache" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222725" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/wpsupercache-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Super Cache is a popular <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-caching-plugins-compared/" title="7 Best WordPress Caching Plugins Compared (2018)">caching plugin for WordPress</a> sites. It&#8217;s free to download and use. It comes with amazing caching features that&#8217;ll help you improve the performance of your nonprofit website.</p>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wp-super-cache/" title="WP Super Cache Review 2018: Is It the Best WordPress Caching Plugin?">WP Super Cache</a> offers page cache, CDN support, cache pre-loading, gzip compression, and more. It&#8217;s easy to set up and all settings are beginner-friendly.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/" target="_blank" title="Sucuri Scanner" rel="nofollow">7. Sucuri</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/sucuri/" target="_blank" title="Sucuri Scanner" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri.jpg" alt="Sucuri" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222080" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/sucuri-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Sucuri is the top <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-security-plugins-compared/" title="6 Best WordPress Security Plugins Compared (2018)">WordPress security plugin</a>. It creates a secure wall between your users and your website to protect you from unwanted visitors. <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/sucuri/" title="Sucuri Review 2018: Why We Love Sucuri + Pros and Cons">Sucuri</a> has amazing features that&#8217;ll keep your website secure from malware and hackers.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a recommended plugin for nonprofit sites who accept online donations to maintain security for your donors.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/updraftplus/" target="_blank" title="UpdraftPlus" rel="nofollow">8. UpdraftPlus</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/updraftplus/" target="_blank" title="UpdraftPlus" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus.jpg" alt="UpdraftPlus" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222079" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/updraftplus-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>UpdraftPlus is a popular <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-backup-plugins-compared/" title="9 Best WordPress Backup Plugins Compared (2018)">backup plugin for WordPress</a> sites. It allows you to easily <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/easily-backup-wordpress-site-step-step/" title="How to Easily Back Up Your WordPress Site (Step by Step)">back up your WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve created your nonprofit site, you&#8217;ll want to make sure it&#8217;s up and running, always. <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/updraftplus-review/" title="UpdraftPlus Review: Is It the Best WordPress Backup Plugin?">UpdraftPlus</a> helps you maintain regular backups of your site. It also allows you to easily restore your site from the backups anytime you need to.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/" target="_blank" title="Yoast SEO" rel="nofollow">9. Yoast SEO</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/wordpress-seo/" target="_blank" title="Yoast SEO" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo.jpg" alt="Yoast SEO" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222083" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/yoastseo-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Yoast SEO is the most popular WordPress SEO plugin on the market. It helps you optimize your website for search engines, so you&#8217;ll attract the best visitors who actually want to support your cause. <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/yoast-seo/" title="Yoast SEO Review 2018: Is It the Best WordPress SEO Plugin?">Yoast SEO</a> has many features that can be used to improve your search engine rankings.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/" target="_blank" title="Envira Gallery" rel="nofollow">10. Envira Gallery</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/envira-gallery/" target="_blank" title="Envira Gallery" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery.jpg" alt="Envira Gallery" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222078" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/enviragallery-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Envira Gallery is one of the top <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-gallery-plugins-compared/" title="7 Best WordPress Gallery Plugins Compared (2018)">WordPress image gallery plugins</a>. Many nonprofits want to show their images to new visitors to convince them to donate, which is why <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/envira-gallery/" title="Envira Gallery Review 2018 – The Best WordPress Gallery Plugin">Envira Gallery</a> is an important plugin for the nonprofit sites.</p>\n<p>It allows you to present your photos in beautiful, professional image galleries. It has amazing features like lightbox popup, masonry galleries, polaroid effects, and more.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/" target="_blank" title="Testimonials Widget" rel="nofollow">11. Testimonials Widget</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/testimonials-widget/" target="_blank" title="Testimonials Widget" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets.jpg" alt="Testimonials Widget" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222727" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/testimonialwidgets-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Testimonials Widget is a free WordPress testimonials plugin. It&#8217;s important for nonprofit sites to display testimonials from their donors. The plugin is beginner-friendly and easy to set up.</p>\n<p>It allows you to show testimonials anywhere, including posts, pages, and widget-ready areas. You can add the testimonials widget in your sidebar, footer, or any other widget-supported sections in WordPress.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/" target="_blank" title="Quick and Easy FAQs" rel="nofollow">12. Quick and Easy FAQs</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/quick-and-easy-faqs/" target="_blank" title="Quick and Easy FAQs" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs.jpg" alt="Quick and Easy FAQs" width="785" height="405" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222728" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs.jpg 785w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/quickeasyfaqs-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 785px) 100vw, 785px" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name suggests, Quick and Easy FAQs is an easy-to-use WordPress FAQs plugin. You can use this plugin to add frequently asked questions, with answers, onto your nonprofit site. It saves the time for you and your visitors. The plugin has many templates to present FAQs beautifully.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/tablepress/" target="_blank" title="TablePress" rel="nofollow">13. TablePress</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/tablepress/" target="_blank" title="TablePress" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress.jpg" alt="TablePress" width="775" height="356" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222729" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress-300x138.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/tablepress-768x353.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>TablePress is a free WordPress plugin to add tables, using a simple drag and drop interface, on your site. You can use these tables on your nonprofit site to display donation charts and other stats to your visitors.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-calendar-events/" target="_blank" title="Simple Calendar – Google Calendar Plugin" rel="nofollow">14. Simple Calendar</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/google-calendar-events/" target="_blank" title="Simple Calendar – Google Calendar Plugin" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar.jpg" alt="Simple Calendar" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222730" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/simplecalendar-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Simple Calendar is a Google Calendar plugin that lets you to create events and display them on your nonprofit site. It allows your visitors to subscribe to the calendar, and they&#8217;ll get notifications for new events.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/forget-about-shortcode-buttons/" target="_blank" title="Forget About Shortcode Buttons" rel="nofollow">15. Forget About Shortcode Buttons</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/forget-about-shortcode-buttons/" target="_blank" title="Forget About Shortcode Buttons" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons.jpg" alt="Forget About Shortcode Buttons" width="775" height="396" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222739" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons-300x153.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/forgetaboutshortcodebuttons-768x392.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Forget About Shortcode Buttons is a free WordPress plugin to add stunning buttons onto your nonprofit site. You need to add multiple call-to-action buttons on different pages and posts to make people visit your <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/" title="7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert (2018)">landing pages</a> or donation forms. This unique plugin will help you easily add buttons without the help of shortcodes.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/" target="_blank" title="Polylang" rel="nofollow">16. Polylang</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/" target="_blank" title="Polylang" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang.jpg" alt="Polylang" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222744" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/polylang-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Polylang is a WordPress plugin that offers bilingual and multilingual support. It allows you to <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/" title="How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)">create a multilingual nonprofit site</a>, so anyone in the world can read and follow your content in their own language. It allows your visitors to easily switch the website&#8217;s language into their own language.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/floating-social-bar/" target="_blank" title="Floating Social bar" rel="nofollow">17. Floating Social bar</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/floating-social-bar/" target="_blank" title="Floating Social bar" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar.jpg" alt="Floating Social Bar" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222748" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/floatingsocialbar-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>If you want to add social sharing buttons onto your WordPress site in a beautiful and modern style, then you&#8217;ll need the <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/floating-social-bar/" title="Floating Social Bar">Floating Social Bar</a> plugin. It&#8217;s a free <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-social-media-plugins/" title="12 Best WordPress Social Media Plugins (2018)">social sharing plugin</a> for nonprofit sites to easily share their cause on social media platforms. Your visitors can share the pages and posts on social media channels quickly with just 1 click.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/" target="_blank" title="Revive Old Post" rel="nofollow">18. Revive Old Post</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/tweet-old-post/" target="_blank" title="Revive Post" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg" alt="Revive Post" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222749" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/revivepost-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Revive Old Post is another interesting WordPress plugin that automatically shares your old posts on social media. It saves you time via its automation process. You should use this plugin on your nonprofit site to promote your old posts and keep your social sites engaged.</p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/mappress-google-maps-for-wordpress/" target="_blank" title="MapPress Maps" rel="nofollow">19. MapPress Google Maps</a></h3>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress.jpg" alt="MapPress Google Maps" width="775" height="400" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-222750" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mappress-768x396.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></p>\n<p>MapPress Google Maps is a WordPress plugin for sharing the location of your nonprofit centre. It features easy-to-embed maps that you can place on your WordPress pages and posts. It allows you to mark destinations, add directions, and more.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find best WordPress plugins for nonprofits. You should also check out our hand-picked <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/" title="50+ Best Responsive WordPress Themes">best responsive WordPress themes</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/">19 Best WordPress Plugins for Non-profits &#038; Charities</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-plugins-nonprofits/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"How to Properly Add Code Snippets to Your WordPress Site";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:65:"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:73:"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 19:35:44 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:19:"WordPress Tutorials";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"code snippets";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"functions.php";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:20:"site specific plugin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"template files";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:19:"wordpress templates";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223876";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:625:"<p>Want to know the proper way to add custom code snippets to your WordPress site? Adding code snippets to WordPress isn’t rocket science, but even the slightest mistake could crash your website. If you jump in without knowing what you&#8217;re doing, it could be fatal to your business. So, when you’re adding custom code to [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/">How to Properly Add Code Snippets to Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"Editorial Team";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8991:"<p>Want to know the proper way to add custom code snippets to your WordPress site? Adding code snippets to WordPress isn’t rocket science, but even the slightest mistake could crash your website. If you jump in without knowing what you&#8217;re doing, it could be fatal to your business.</p>\n<p>So, when you’re adding custom code to your site, you’ll need to make sure you’re doing it the RIGHT WAY.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll explain how to properly copy and paste code snippets to your WordPress site. Once you&#8217;ve finished reading, you&#8217;ll have the knowledge and the confidence to modify your site as you please. You might even have a bit of FUN!</p>\n<h3>Why Add Code Snippets to WordPress?</h3>\n<p>Adding code snippets to your site is one of the easiest ways to extend your website’s features. Although installing a plugin is the obvious way to enhance the built-in features of WordPress, especially for non-developers, at times, it’s hard to find a plugin that addresses your needs to the letter. On the other hand, you can find hundreds of WordPress tutorials on the web that recommend adding code snippets to meet your needs.</p>\n<p>That said, it’s essential for you to properly insert the custom code snippets in the correct file and in the right location. Otherwise, it could crash your website, in turn sabotaging your business and reputation.</p>\n<p>Let’s break down this tutorial into 2 different sections:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Customizing WordPress template files</li>\n<li>Customizing functions.php file</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>I. Customizing WordPress Template Files</h3>\n<p>Before we dive in, let’s take a look at what a WordPress template file is.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s a WordPress Template?</strong></p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/customize-a-template.png" alt="customize a template" width="740" height="379" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223878" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/customize-a-template.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/customize-a-template-300x154.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px" /></p>\n<p>Every WordPress theme is made up of template files. The template files on your theme define how your website is displayed. For example, header.php is a default template used in most WordPress themes to define the header area of your WordPress-generated web pages, such as your blog articles and standalone pages.</p>\n<p>Let’s take a look at a few default WordPress templates used by most WordPress themes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>php – defines the main page</li>\n<li>php – defines the header section</li>\n<li>php – defines the footer section</li>\n<li>php – defines the functions used in the theme</li>\n<li>php – defines the single post / blog post</li>\n<li>php – defines the standalone page</li>\n<li>php – defines the comments section</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Insert Snippets Into Any Template File</h3>\n<p>You can insert code snippets into any template file, such as functions.php, single.php, etc. by either of these 2 methods: by using a child theme or by adding the code directly to your existing parent theme.</p>\n<p>However, it’s advised not to customize the template directly in your parent theme because, when you upgrade your theme, you’ll lose all the customizations you’ve made. To preserve the tweaks even after upgrading your theme, you might want to create a child theme and make customization within it.</p>\n<p>A child theme is a WordPress theme that inherits its functionality from another WordPress theme (the parent theme). Using a child theme is the right choice if you want to make a lot of tweaks to your template files.</p>\n<p>Let’s take a look at how to create a child theme and insert snippets into your template file.</p>\n<p>For a detailed guide, you can check out <a href="https://www.wpbeginner.com/wp-themes/how-to-create-a-wordpress-child-theme-video/">how to create a child theme on WordPress</a>.</p>\n<h3>II. Customizing functions.php file</h3>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s functions.php file?</strong></p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/functions.php-file.png" alt="functions.php file" width="740" height="397" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223879" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/functions.php-file.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/functions.php-file-300x161.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px" /></p>\n<p>functions.php is a template file in your WordPress theme that enables you to easily extend the features of your theme and WordPress installation. To extend the features, all you have to do is add certain code snippets to your functions.php file.</p>\n<p>Just like any other template files, you can add snippets directly to your functions.php file. In addition, to retain the customization even after upgrading your theme, you can create a child theme and insert the code within it.</p>\n<p>However, the downside is that you’ll lose all the customization you’ve made on a child theme if you switch over to a new/different theme. This is where a site-specific plugin comes in.</p>\n<p>A site-specific WordPress plugin is independent of your theme, which allows you to add custom snippets to your site. You can use site-specific plugin in 2 ways:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Method #1: Using a ready-made plugin, such as Code Snippets</li>\n<li>Method #2: Manually creating a site-specific plugin</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Method #1: Using a Readymade Plugin</h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/code-snippets/">Code Snippets</a> is a <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/">WordPress plugin</a> that provides a graphical interface for managing snippets similar to the Plugins menu.</p>\n<p>It removes the need to insert custom snippets to your theme’s functions.php file. Since you’re not inserting the code in any theme files, you can preserve the customization on your site even after switching your theme.</p>\n<p>With Code Snippets, you can activate or deactivate snippets, just like plugins.</p>\n<p>Once you’ve activated <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/code-snippets/">the Code Snippets plugin</a>, you can add custom snippets, and then specify a title, description, and tags for the snippets as reference for yourself down the line. That way, in the future, you can easily figure out the purpose of each snippet you&#8217;ve added.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2.png" alt="" width="727" height="415" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223697" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2.png 727w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2-300x171.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 727px) 100vw, 727px" /></p>\n<p>For more details, you can read our post on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/">how to create a site-specific plugin</a>.</p>\n<h3>2. Create a Site-Specific Plan and Insert the Code</h3>\n<p>You can manually create a site-specific plugin and insert the code within it. Unlike a ready-made plugin, a manually-created site-specific plugin is usually a basic, lightweight plugin that doesn’t have a graphical interface for managing snippets.</p>\n<p>To make customizations, you can head over to the plugin editor and insert the code into it.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin.png" alt="add your snippets to site-specific plugin" width="748" height="378" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223677" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin.png 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin-300x152.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px" /></p>\n<p>For a step-by-step guide, you can check out <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/">creating a site-specific plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>That’s it!</p>\n<p>We hope this guide helped you add code snippets to your <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/">WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, go ahead and <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/snippets/">find some code snippets</a> that you can add to enhance your WordPress&#8217; functionalities.</p>\n<p>If you liked this article, you may also want to check out <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/must-have-wordpress-plugins-for-business-websites/">must-have plugins for business website</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/">How to Properly Add Code Snippets to Your WordPress Site</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:70:"https://www.isitwp.com/properly-add-code-snippets-wordpress-site/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:51:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"How to Create a Multi-Page Form in WordPress (Step by Step)";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"https://www.isitwp.com/create-multi-page-form-wordpress/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:64:"https://www.isitwp.com/create-multi-page-form-wordpress/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 26 Oct 2018 10:28:36 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:19:"WordPress Tutorials";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:23:"create a wordpress form";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"multi-page form";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"wpforms";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:32:"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=221865";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:616:"<p>Are you looking to create a multi-page form in WordPress? Great idea! Multi-page forms are a fantastic way to gather information and keep your visitors engaged with your site. In this article, we’ll show you how to create a multi-page form in WordPress the easy way. Why Use Multi-Page Forms? Have you ever gotten annoyed [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-multi-page-form-wordpress/">How to Create a Multi-Page Form in WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:14:"Editorial Team";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7707:"<p>Are you looking to create a multi-page form in WordPress? Great idea! Multi-page forms are a fantastic way to gather information and keep your visitors engaged with your site.</p>\n<p>In this article, we’ll show you how to create a multi-page form in WordPress the easy way.</p>\n<h3>Why Use Multi-Page Forms?</h3>\n<p>Have you ever gotten annoyed by a website with a long form you’ve had to fill out? Of course you have. We’ve all been there.</p>\n<p>In order to avoid “form fatigue” in your users, you can break up your long forms into multiple pages. This gives you the power to ask the questions you need answered in bite-sized chunks. That way, your website visitors won’t feel annoyed or overwhelmed.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/why-use-a-multi-page-form.png" alt="why use a multi-page form" width="562" height="368" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223645" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/why-use-a-multi-page-form.png 562w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/why-use-a-multi-page-form-300x196.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px" /></p>\n<p>Using multi-page forms (like the example above) when asking for a ton of information decreases the rate of form abandonment, thus upping your conversion rates. Plus, if someone is willing to fill out a multi-page form, it shows their dedication to your website, which makes them a higher quality lead.</p>\n<p>Higher quality, pre-qualified, leads mean more sales in the long run.</p>\n<p>So, without further ado, let’s get you on the right track and create your first multi-page form!</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Create a Multi-Page Form in WordPress</h3>\n<p>The easiest way to make a multi-page form in WordPress is to use the <a href="https://wpforms.com/" target="_blank">WPForms plugin</a>. It’s the most beginner-friendly <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/">contact form plugin</a> on the market, and the most reliable. You’ll need to purchase it before we begin.</p>\n<p><a href="https://wpforms.com/" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png" alt="WPForms" width="775" height="350" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-218485" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/wpforms-768x347.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Fortunately, IsItWP users can use the coupon code <strong>SAVE10</strong> to get a 10 percent discount on any version of <a href="https://wpforms.com/" target="_blank">WPForms</a>. (You’ll need at least the Basic version for this tutorial).</p>\n<p>After you purchase the plugin, go ahead and install and activate it. Not sure how to install and activate a plugin? No problem! We wrote <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/">a guide for that</a>.</p>\n<p>After activation, head to <strong>WPForms &raquo; Settings</strong> and verify your product with the license key you were given. </p>\n<p>Then, go to <strong>WPForms &raquo; Add New</strong> to start building your form.</p>\n<p>From here, you can either choose a template that resembles what you’d like your form to look like, or start one from scratch. After clicking on your selection, you can modify it by dragging and dropping fields from the left-hand panel onto your form.</p>\n<p>After the first page of your form looks the way you want it, go ahead and click on the <strong>Pagebreak</strong> field under the Fancy Fields section in the left-hand panel. This will add a pagebreak marker, and a “Next” button, to your form.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/insert-page-break.png" alt="insert pagebreak" width="775" height="357" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223646" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/insert-page-break.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/insert-page-break-300x138.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/insert-page-break-768x354.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></p>\n<p>There will also be a <strong>First Page</strong> marker at the top of your form. Click on it to edit your multi-page form properties.</p>\n<p>In the left-hand panel, you can select a progress bar in the form of a bar, a circle, a connector, or none at all. We’ll be using the Connectors progress bar type for this tutorial.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/edit-progress-bar.png" alt="edit progress bar" width="775" height="242" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223647" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/edit-progress-bar.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/edit-progress-bar-300x94.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/edit-progress-bar-768x240.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></p>\n<p>You can also choose your page indicator’s color, and provide a title for your first page.</p>\n<p>Next, click on the pagebreak marker to edit it. Here, you can title the next page. You can also edit the “Next” button to display any text you’d like.</p>\n<p>From there, you can add additional fields to your form after the pagebreak. And, if you’re using the Pro version (or better) of WPForms, you can opt to use conditional logic to hide and show form fields based on your users’ responses.</p>\n<p>Continue adding pagebreaks and form fields for as many pages as necessary. Simply repeat the above steps until you have the form length you’d like.</p>\n<p>Once you’ve finished, click <strong>Save</strong> at the top right-hand corner of your screen. Congrats! The “hard” part is over! </p>\n<p>Now it’s time to move onto the final step.</p>\n<h3>Step 2: Add Your Multi-Page Form to Posts and Pages</h3>\n<p>With WPForms, you can add forms to posts or pages with 3 clicks.</p>\n<p>First, create a new page or post. Then, click the <strong>Add Form</strong> button above your toolbar.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/add-form.png" alt="add form" width="775" height="265" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223648" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/add-form.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/add-form-300x103.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/add-form-768x263.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></p>\n<p>Click on the form you created from the dropdown menu. Then, click <strong>Add Form</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/insert-form.png" alt="insert form" width="500" height="301" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223649" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/insert-form.png 500w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/insert-form-300x181.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /></p>\n<p>Publish your post or page and you’re done. Good to go.</p>\n<p>That’s it! Seriously! Rock on.</p>\n<p>We hope this tutorial helped you create a multi-page form in WordPress with ease. If you liked this article, you might also enjoy our tutorial on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-survey-in-wordpress/">how to create a survey in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/create-multi-page-form-wordpress/">How to Create a Multi-Page Form in WordPress (Step by Step)</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRs