 for hiring and your work. Moreover, it has a simple list blog layout, animated banner, about us, services, work and portfolio with fancybox, counter up, experience timeline, client and footer widgets. </p>\n<p>With iThemer, you can use Google fonts, Font Awesome icons, social links, etc. and show off your creativity. </p>\n<p>The theme allows you to import the demo content with 1 click and get started with your resume site instantly. For customizing the theme options and design, you can use the Live Customizer which lets you customize your site with real-time live previews. </p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/ithemer/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with iThemer today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomic/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">21. Atomic</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomic/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="atomic-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="452" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223257" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Atomic is a multipurpose WordPress theme suitable for creating a portfolio as well as a business website. It comes with beautiful templates for teams, services, testimonials, portfolio, blog posts, and more. </p>\n<p>The theme has stylish typography and intuitive organization for its different site elements. It allows full customization of your site&#8217;s header by changing a header image, background color, image opacity, text, etc. </p>\n<p>Most importantly, to let you showcase your latest projects, it has options to add image galleries, videos, etc. in different styles. </p>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomic/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with Atomic today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/excellent/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">22. Excellent</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/excellent/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="excellent-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="452" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223258" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Excellent is a freemium <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/">responsive theme</a> for creating professional business, blog, CV, and portfolio sites. It comes with a full set of excellent features that enable you to build a great-looking resume site in no time.</p>\n<p>The theme features cool templates for portfolio, gallery, blog, testimonials, contact us, etc. You can also find custom widgets, multiple navigation and social menus, and endless color options to make your site’s design unique. </p>\n<p>It has a handy demo for a standard CV that has a profile photo and profile details in 2 columns on the homepage. Below that, there’s a beautiful portfolio section to showcase your latest work. </p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/excellent/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with Excellent today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-eclipse/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">23. Eclipse</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-eclipse/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="eclipse-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="452" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223134" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re a photographer and looking for a theme to showcase your wonderful photos, Eclipse is the perfect theme for you. The theme comes with beautiful slider options in the header, image galleries, portfolio posts, and cute blog templates. </p>\n<p>The theme provides options to add widgets in the homepage where you can add any widget you like including your about page, Instagram widget, buy option for your photo prints, etc. The theme is WooCommerce-ready so you can create a shop page and sell your photographs. </p>\n<p>Eclipse has built-in Live Customizer which allows you to change the design of your site with immediate live previews. Therefore, it’s easy and quick to customize the theme. </p>\n<p><a href="https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-eclipse/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with Eclipse today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">24. Libretto</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="libretto-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="452" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223259" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Libretto is a free responsive 1-column theme for WordPress. It features a classic style and careful typography details so that your site content looks classy. It’s ideal for showcasing articles with large images or for photo stories with inspirational quotes. So, if you’re an inspirational photographer, it’s a perfect theme to start your resume website. </p>\n<p>Libretto provides beautiful templates for blog, about, and contact page.  The theme is so simple and easy to use that even a person with absolutely no coding skills can build a complete site using this theme. </p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with Libretto today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">25. Resumee</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="resumee-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="475" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223260" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme-300x184.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme-768x471.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Resumee is simple WordPress resume theme for professionals. It has a clean design with an all white background. You can add a profile photo, social links, contact details, and a short bio at the top of your homepage. </p>\n<p>It’s basically a 1-page theme with different sections for work experience, education, and skills right on the homepage. It’s a direct and distraction-free minimalist resume theme. </p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with Resume today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/idyllic/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">26. Idyllic</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/idyllic/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="idyllic-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="475" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223261" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme-300x184.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme-768x471.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Idyllic is a beautiful multipurpose theme for WordPress that you can use for creating a variety of websites. With its extended features and options, you can use it for business, portfolio, blog, or online resume website. </p>\n<p>The theme comes with multiple sections as well as widgets on the front page. There’re multiple navigation and social menus, logo upload, and color options. For showcasing your selected works and latest projects, it has several fabulous portfolio layouts. </p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/idyllic/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with Idyllic today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/orfeo/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">27. Orfeo</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/orfeo/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="orfeo-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="443" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223262" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme-300x171.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme-768x439.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>Orfeo is a responsive 1-page WordPress theme designed for multipurpose sites. You can build corporate business sites as well as a blog, portfolio, or online resume site using this theme. It features beautifully-designed sections for features, team, testimonials, products, pricing, blog, contact, etc. </p>\n<p>If you’re an entrepreneur, blogger, or a student, this theme provides you with ample features to create your impressive online portfolio. You can use custom backgrounds, mega menus, etc. and customize the entire theme&#8217;s options from its Live Customizer. </p>\n<p>It’s an SEO optimized and fast loading theme that lets you create a truly powerful site. </p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/orfeo/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with Orfeo today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/mcluhan/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">28. McLuhan</a></h3>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/mcluhan/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme.jpg" alt="mcluhan-wordpress-theme" width="775" height="455" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-223263" srcset="https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme-300x176.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme-768x451.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px" /></a></p>\n<p>McLuhan is a free WordPress theme with a simple and clean design. It features a front page with a complete post archive arranged by year to give your users a quick glimpse of your work via the custom timeline. </p>\n<p>With McLuhan, you can get 2 predefined page templates: a resume page template and a full-width template. Using the resume template, you can easily create your online resume. </p>\n<p>The theme allows you to customize background colors for the sidebar and content, plus add social links and icons. It has an AJAX-powered mobile search with instant results. </p>\n<p><a href="https://wordpress.org/themes/mcluhan/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Get started with McLuhan today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best WordPress resume themes for creating an online resume, CV, and portfolio. You may also want to see our guide on <a href="https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/">how to make money from online blogging</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/">28 Best WordPress Resume Themes to Create Best Impression</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.isitwp.com">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:54:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:55:"WPForms vs. Gravity Forms – Best Form Plugin Showdown";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"https://www.isitwp.com/wpforms-vs-gravity-forms/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"https://www.isitwp.com/wpforms-vs-gravity-forms/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s: