(4345, 48, '2018-10-31 08:36:32', '2018-10-31 08:36:32', '[vc_row full_width="stretch_row" full_height="yes" parallax="content-moving" parallax_image="3705" css=".vc_custom_1493378039456{background-color: #f5f5ed !important;background-position: center;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][vc_column 0=""][vc_custom_heading text="I am Digital Nomad" font_container="tag:h1|font_size:130|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff" google_fonts="font_family:Unna%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal" css=".vc_custom_1493290318099{margin-top: 0px !important;}"][vc_btn title="Biography of Kim Yuna" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#ffffff" outline_custom_hover_background="#0000d3" outline_custom_hover_text="#ffffff" shape="square" size="lg" align="center" link="|||"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1493295493496{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}"][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_separator color="custom" align="align_left" border_width="3" el_width="10" accent_color="#0000d3"][vc_custom_heading text="To Live &amp; Travel" font_container="tag:h2|font_size:60|text_align:left|color:%23595959" google_fonts="font_family:Unna%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal"][vc_column_text 0=""]\n<p style="text-align: left;">For me, traveling is a way of living from the very childhood. My father was a pro stuntman and mother a writer. We moved from state to state every two or three month. Now I am a full-time travel blogger and digital artist working for a various digital agencies and travel journals across the US.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">A website ... well, I need to have a tool that is able to help me to update information quickly on the go. I want to be able to post photos from the temple of Katmandu or write an article on how I spent a night with bootleggers in Tennessee.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner 0=""][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="UI/UX Expert" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:40|text_align:left|color:%23595959" google_fonts="font_family:Unna%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal"][vc_column_text 0=""]An expert in digital media, I will be able to help you to build a sustainable strategy and implement it via visual tools.\n\nFrom UX and up to UI, you will receive a full service to ensure you are connected to your customers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_custom_heading text="Travel Away" font_container="tag:h3|font_size:40|text_align:left|color:%23595959" google_fonts="font_family:Unna%3Aregular|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal"][vc_column_text 0=""]Make sure to follow my path around the world to see the most awesome destinations. From the snowy hills of Iceland and up to The Gobi desert.\n\nLove to travel? Drop me a message and we can make your trip together.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1493295465969{padding-top: 25px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;background-color: #0000d3 !important;}"][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_icon type="linecons" icon_linecons="vc_li vc_li-pen" color="white" size="lg" align="center"][vc_column_text 0=""]\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">An award of excellence in design and named as creative of the year.</span></p>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_icon type="linecons" icon_linecons="vc_li vc_li-location" color="white" size="lg" align="center"][vc_column_text 0=""]\n<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">An expert of local spots and hidden attractions.</span></p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title="Get Visual Composer Now" style="outline-custom" outline_custom_color="#ffffff" outline_custom_hover_background="#ffffff" outline_custom_hover_text="#595959" shape="square" size="lg" align="center" link="